c: 17
v: 25
t: "Sinaamey sin Rabbi sin nafsittee kee sin sorkocobbaxittet taniimit ixxigah siinik yayseh maqaane tekkek hinnay umaane tekkek, isin meqe maray niya kak temqeeh sinni xaleynah yamqeeh Yallâ fanah gaca tekkeenik, toysa diggah sin Rabbi faxe waktiiy takkay isil gaca marah dambi cabe kinni"